ss=\"red\">但如果僱員要求</span></span></strong>，僱主可按下列方式給予年假：<br />\n - 年假日數不超過 10天 : 可將不多於3天的假期分開發放，而餘下的年假則應連續發放。<br />\n - 年假日數超過 10天 : 最少連續發放7天年假，餘下的年假可以分開發放。"},{"pid":"b789165fc5a9d8326bff6f240f336b6ca43561c8","tid":2230969,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"316f1408ffe1a901f1468e969669ee28b29a83b0","tid":2230969,"uid":107927,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T10:27:27.000Z","msg":"僱員須於隨後 12 個月之內放取應得的有薪年假。<br />\n<br />\n年假日數超過 10 天<br />\r\n最少連續發放 7 天年假，餘下的年<br />\r\n假可分開發放"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T14:15:22.000Z","msg":"連放7日係僱員可以要求連放<br />\n唔係僱主強制員工一定要連放7日<br />\n搞清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"502b3c30b2e3c9415f6053aa1fc3b57344340d2e","tid":2230969,"uid":107927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b789165fc5a9d8326bff6f240f336b6ca43561c8","tid":2230969,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"316f1408ffe1a901f1468e969669ee28b29a83b0","tid":2230969,"uid":107927,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T10:27:27.000Z","msg":"僱員須於隨後 12 個月之內放取應得的有薪年假。<br />\n<br />\n年假日數超過 10 天<br />\r\n最少連續發放 7 天年假，餘下的年<br />\r\n假可分開發放"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T14:15:22.000Z","msg":"連放7日係僱員可以要求連放<br />\n唔係僱主強制員工一定要連放7日<br />\n搞清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T15:12:12.000Z","msg":"法例係咁寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你估僱主想僱員放大假咩。<br />\n一陣僱員自己唔放連假，轉頭告鳩僱主咪仆街。"},{"pid":"4b50ded75954a9336a30ed53c407abab88ba35cc","tid":2230969,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"502b3c30b2e3c9415f6053aa1fc3b57344340d2e","tid":2230969,"uid":107927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b789165fc5a9d8326bff6f240f336b6ca43561c8","tid":2230969,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"316f1408ffe1a901f1468e969669ee28b29a83b0","tid":2230969,"uid":107927,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score